  <brief_title>The Eurocyst Initiative: Building a Network of ADPKD Reference Centers Across Europe</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Eurocyst Initiative: Building a Reference Center Network Across EUROpe to Establish a Large-scale Longitudinal Observational Cohort of Autosomal Dominant polyCYSTic Kidney Disease (ADPKD) Patients</official_title>
